    <a class="action-card" href="SATOI_Mock_v1_B3_treatment_detail.html?cancer=lung"><div class="action-card-icon">📋</div><div class="action-card-title">治療レジメンの詳細</div><div class="action-card-desc">具体的な薬と副作用</div></a>
    <a class="action-card" href="SATOI_Mock_v1_CHP_consider.html"><div class="action-card-icon">🧭</div><div class="action-card-title">治療を考える</div><div class="action-card-desc">SDM・セカンドオピニオン</div></a>
